\id 2TH - TEKE MUKAANA A POOLE WU A MYELE KUNDAA BASI TESALONIKE 
\h 2 TESALONIKE 
\toc3 2 Tes 
\toc2 2 Tesalonike 
\toc1 MUKAANA A POOLE WU A MYELE KUNDAA BASI TESALONIKE 
\mt2 MUKAANA A POOLE WU A MYELE KUNDAA BASI 
\mt1 TESALONIKE 
\imt1 OSOMO 
\ip Wu me mukaana wu a buolo wu ósono Poole kundaa banga-a-kana ba bali ku bvulu lili Tesalonike. Munsa mukaana wu, Poole li mu ofirikalyele bo mandagha ma matala obvughuru o Kriste ya bu ookala masini ma baara ba baakasa kana mu nde. Mu kuulu, baara bana munsa bvulu li Tesalonike bákalyele ti Kriste áyi amaayabvughuru. Baara babake bákalyele ti nde nkini ka áyabvughuru o, lo etsughu ki aayabvughuru nde eebehene. 
\ip Babo ba bákalyele ti etsughu ki ooyabvughuru Kriste eebehene bákabihi osala. Bo bákalyele ti kala bo basala, esala e bo sa ekala kii bwunu. Lo bo bákayidza kundaa babo ba bákasala. Me mu obo Poole ásono bo mukaana mu osuo bo ti nswe mbwuru faana ota tsughuru mu obagha bi-odza. 
\ip Nde ályele bo si ti mu matala ma baamono bo mpara bo bafaana ogwama ya osa mukama mu okasa bubwe. 
\ib  
\iot Bu me bu baakakaba mukaana wu: 
\io1 - Mboro (\xt 1.1-2\xt*) 
\io1 - Oyabvughuru o Yiisu ŋa nsie sa otwulu bilogho byehene mu bunsumu (\xt 1.3-12\xt*) 
\io1 - Mfumu Yiisu nkini aayabvughuru o (\xt 2.1-12\xt*) 
\io1 - Ogwama mu kana (\xt 2.13-17\xt*) 
\io1 - Lisamana ya esala (\xt 3.1-15\xt*) 
\io1 - Mboro yi masini (\xt 3.16-18\xt*). 
\ie  
\c 1  
\s1 Mamboro 
\p  
\v 1 Me Poole, emõ ya Silibvĩ ya Timote, lisono mukaana wu kundaa libwunu li Nzaami li lili mu bvulu lili Tesalonike, libwunu li Nzaami Taara a bihi ya lili Mfumu Yiisu-Kriste:  
\v 2 Nyaã bwehe ya edzuunu bi bifi kundaa Nzaami Taara a bihi ya kundaa Mfumu Yiisu-Kriste bikala ya be! 
\s1 Mumfwunu wu aakala mu etsughu ki oogya Kriste 
\p  
\v 3 Bandughu ba me mu kana, mu nswe matala, bihi lifaana okabvurulu matuono kundaa Nzaami mu be. Oli bubwe kundaa bihi mu okasa obo, mu kuulu kana li be lili mu okakulu ku olagha, ya dzyi li lili a be bwohono bana ya babamo lili mu okapfini.  
\v 4 Me mu obo bihi lili a mutwunu mu okabili mu be mu mabwunu ma Nzaami, mu nkooro a mukama ya kana li be ŋa nkulu a bigyeele byehene ya kimini bi liikabwana a be.  
\v 5 Ekye me elyimi kii mumfwunu a Nzaami wu bunsumu, mpaala be likala baara baba mukughu mu Emfumu e Nzaami kiili, be lili mu okamono mpara mu kye.  
\v 6 Mu kuulu kala oli ngaŋma ti Nzaami li bunsumu, nde sa abvurulu mpara kundaa babo ba baakamwehẽ be mpara.  
\v 7 Mu matala ma oomoŋono Mfumu Yiisu, ŋa akala aafa nde ku yulu ya bangye-yulu ba nde baba lileene, Nzaami sa agwa be ogwumu, emõ ya bihi, be ba lili kunsa mpara.  
\v 8 Yiisu sa agya munsa mile mi mbaa, mu osyeme ba bagwene osoolo Nzaami ya ba bagwene a bintamana mu Nsia yi Mbwe yi a Mfumu a bihi Yiisu.  
\v 9 Masyeme ma ofaana obagha baara babo me obyihi kuu mibvu ya mibvu. Bo sa bakala la ya Mfumu ya nsia a mpini a nde.  
\v 10 Mandagha mamo sa makeele mu etsughu ki oogya Mfumu. Mu obo, bwohono ba bali baba ndaa nde sa bagwa nde nsia, bwohono ba baakasa kana sa bagwa nde masyighi. Behe si sa likala emõ ya bo, mu kuulu be liisi kana mu bumpughulu bu liisuo bihi be. 
\p  
\v 11 Me mu obo bihi liikasamana matala mwohono mu be, mu kuulu Nzaami a bihi aamono ti be lili baba mukughu mu mbili yi áti nde be, ya nde akuhu mu lileene li nde, bitsimi byehene bi bibwe ya bigyighili byehene bibi kana,  
\v 12 mpaala nkwumu a Mfumu a bihi Yiisu yikala a nsia mu be, ya be likala mu nde, ti bwunu a bu oli bwehe bu Nzaami a bihi ya Mfumu Yiisu-Kriste. 
\c 2  
\s1 Mandagha ma maamoŋono nsomo Mfumu agya 
\p  
\v 1 Bandughu mu kana, mu mi mitala oyabvughuru o Mfumu Yiisu-Kriste ya obvuŋunu o bihi-a-be ya nde, bihi liluomo be bu:  
\v 2 ka lisa o kuulu ti bitsimi bi be bigwimi maswa-maswa mu nkooro a ndagha yi osuo mufulu, mu ndagha nga-mõ bwunu we mu nkooro a mukaana wu baalyele ti kundaa bihi aafi, wu li mu okalyele ti etsughu e Mfumu eeto.  
\v 3 Mbwuru anyaã opfiri be mu ndagha si mõ. Nsomo etsughu ekye egya, baara sa batemene a Nzaami nsumu, ya Mbwuru wu Mubi wu obyii sa amoŋono.  
\v 4 Nde sa atemene nsumu ya byene bi baakata ti nzaami, bwunu we byehene bi baakasyighi. Nde sa ato tee mu eteese kii oyibwa nsini mu Nzo a Nzaami, ya ki olyele ndeme ti nde me Nzaami. 
\p  
\v 5 Be ka lili mu olibili mweẽ o ti me áli andyele be ndagha yi ŋa ándi me nkini kundaa be?  
\v 6 Ya mu matala ma be ligyighili osoolo emakye eli mu okakwara nde, mpaala nde amoŋono yini a mu matala ma bákuru.  
\v 7 Mu kuulu mansweghe ma bubi mali mu okabulusala, lo sa masomo mu osala ku obvulu ŋa odzimini munde wu li mu okakwara nde.  
\v 8 Mu obo Mbwuru wu Mubi sa amoŋono, lo Mfumu Yiisu sa adzwa nde mu mufulu a muŋma a nde ya sa akala adzihibi nde mu matala ma aamoŋono nde.  
\v 9 Ogya o Mbwuru wu Mubi sa omoŋono mu lileene lili Satana, mu mpaana yi mawa-mawa, mu bilyimi ya bimaã bibi mpya,  
\v 10 ya mu opfiri kuu mawa-mawa ya ogwene ku bunsumu kundaa babo ba baagwuŋumu, mu kuulu bo ka baagyagha dzyi lili engaŋma liili áli likughu obvwuhu bo o.  
\v 11 Me mu obo Nzaami li mu ogweghe bo mufulu wu ogwuŋumu mpaala basa kana mu mpya,  
\v 12 mu kuulu basa muyala kundaa baara bwohono baala ka baasi kana mu engaŋma o, lo baala baamono esee mu okagyighili mandagha mama gwene a bunsumu. 
\s1 Nzaami aasuolo be mu obvughu 
\p  
\v 13 Bandughu mu kana ba ookadzyi Mfumu, bihi me baala lifaana okabvurulu matuono kundaa Nzaami matala mwohono mu nkooro a be. Mu kuulu, Nzaami ásuolo be mu okala baba nsomo mu obvwughu, mpaala be libvwughu mu libaha li Mufulu wu aakasa ti be likala baba ngili ya likala a kana mu engaŋma.  
\v 14 Nzaami áti behe si mbili mu nzili a Nsia yi Mbwe yi líluo bihi be, mpaala be libagha nsia a Mfumu a bihi Yiisu-Kriste. 
\p  
\v 15 Me mu obo, bandughu mu kana, lisa mukama ya likwara maluo ma liiluo bihi be, ngu okala mu mbiili bwunu we mu mukaana. 
\p  
\v 16 Nyaã Mfumu a bihi Yiisu-Kriste ndeme ya Nzaami Taara a bihi, wu áadzyi bihi ya wuulu mu bwehe bu nde, aagwi bihi mpama yi a mibvu ya mibvu ya emiini ki ebwe,  
\v 17 bagwa be mpama ya mpini mu okasa bigyighili bi bibwe ya mbiili yi mbwe matala mwohono! 
\c 3  
\s1 Oluomo lisamana 
\p  
\v 1 Mu omana, bandughu mu kana liikasamana Nzaami mu nkooro a bihi, mpaala ndagha a Mfumu yitsaŋama mu maswa-maswa ya yibagha nsia ti anga bu yili a yo nsia kundaa be.  
\v 2 Liikasamana si Nzaami mpaala bihi libvwughu ŋa myaã mi baara ba nga-a-ebaghala ya ba babi, mu kuulu baara bwohono ka bali a kana o. 
\p  
\v 3 Lo Mfumu li wu bakughu osa kana mu nde, nde sa agwa be mpini ya sa akala be mu Nga-a-bubi.  
\v 4 Bihi lili a kana mu Mfumu ti be lili mu okasa ya be sa lifirikasa mandagha mwohono ma lili mu okatumu bihi be. 
\p  
\v 5 Nyaã Mfumu akatumu mikolo mi be mpaala be likadzyi Nzaami ya likala a mukama ti wu a Kriste! 
\s1 Osala mu efaana kii ntumu 
\p  
\v 6 Bandughu mu kana, mu nkwumu a Mfumu a bihi-a-be Yiisu-Kriste, bihi ligwi be litumu mu okala la ya nswe ndughu mu kana wu li mubolo, wu agwene okanama maluo ma liiluo bihi be. 
\p  
\v 7 Be beme lisoolo bu lifaana onama be efaana e bihi, mu kuulu bihi ka liili babolo ŋa kara li be o.  
\v 8 Bihi ka liili bi-odza bi mbwuru ku o bwunu o. Lo kunsa esala ya kunsa mpara, mpyibi ya mwiĩ bihi liikasala mpaala linyaã okala leme kundaa mbwuru mumõ ŋa kara li be.  
\v 9 Ka mu kuulu ti bihi ka liili a muswa o, lo mu kuulu bihi bameme liidzyi osuo be efaana ki lifaana be onama.  
\v 10 Buulu, ŋa líli bihi kundaa be, bihi líkagwa be litumu li: Kala ti mbwuru ka dzyi okasala o, lo anyaã si okadza! 
\p  
\v 11 Lo bihi lili mu okagyughu ti baara bana ŋa kara li be bali kunsa bubolo, ya ŋa ebini kii osala, bo bali okabulunama mandagha ma magwene a mubwughu.  
\v 12 Mu nkwumu a Mfumu a bihi-a-be Yiisu-Kriste, bihi lili mu okagwa litumu ya mpama kundaa baara baba obo, mu okasala mu edzuunu mu kuulu babagha bi-odza mu mpini a bomo.  
\v 13 Lo kundaa be bandughu mu kana, ka likolo mu okasa bubwe o. 
\p  
\v 14 Kala ti mbwuru bihi onama mandagha ma liitumu bihi munsa mukaana wu, lisa kuulu ti baara bwohono basoolo nde ya ka lifirikala a endughu ya nde o, mpaala nde amono bupfiri.  
\v 15 Ka limono nde ti anga mutaara o, lo ligyehe nde ti anga bu baakagyehe ndughu mu kana. 
\s1 Liseme ya mamboro 
\p  
\v 16 Nyaã Mfumu wu edzuunu, ndeme akagwa be edzuunu mu matala mwohono ya mu mandagha mwohono. Nyaã Mfumu akala ya be bwohono! 
\p  
\v 17 Me Poole, me ngwi be mboro, bu nsono yo mu kwogho e meme. Ekye me enyeme ki aakansa me mu mikaana myehene mi aakansono me. 
\p  
\v 18 Nyaã bwehe bu Mfumu a bihi-a-be Yiisu-Kriste bukala ya be bwohono!